    • handleModPartSave

      public void handleModPartSave(javafx.event.ActionEvent event) throws IOException
      Values for the modified part are entered by the user, checking for type mismatches and ensuring that min is less than max. In-House and Outsourced are then checked to ensure that the part is correctly attributed to either field.
      Parameters:
